  (str ministry) (str `Ministry of Ports, Shipping and Waterways`)
  (str department) (undefined)
  (str longTitle) (str `An Act to consolidate and amend the law relating to merchant shipping to ensure compliance with India's obligation under the maritime treaties and international instruments to which India is a party and also to ensure the development of Indian shipping and efficient maintenance of Indian mercantile marine in a manner best suited to serve the national interest and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`)
